'''欣快'''或'''欣快感'''（{{lang-en|euphoria}}，{{IPAc-en|icon|juː|ˈ|f|ɔər|i|ə}}，来源于[[古希腊语|古希腊语]] {{lang|el|εὐφορία}}，“轻松、持久的力量”<ref>[http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/cgi-bin/ptext?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.04.0057%3Aentry%3D%2345426 Euphoria, Henry George Liddell, Robert Scott, ''A Greek-English Lexicon'', at Perseus]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.etymonline.com/index.php?search=euphoria&searchmode=none |title=Online Etymology Dictionary |access-date=2013-04-06 |archive-date=2008-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081221185537/http://www.etymonline.com/index.php?search=euphoria&searchmode=none |dead-url=no }}</ref>，词义与[[烦躁|烦躁]]相反），在[[医学|医学]]上把它当做一种[[精神|精神]]和[[情感|情感]]的状态。心情愉快、无忧无虑、兴高采烈、异常幸福、兴奋、喜悦<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rightdiagnosis.com/sym/euphoria.htm |title=Euphoria - RightDiagnosis.com |access-date=2013-04-06 |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130044916/https://www.rightdiagnosis.com/sym/euphoria.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。从技术上来说，欣快在[[心理学|心理学]]中属于[[行为|行为]]<ref name="DSM4phrases">{{cite web
 |url = http://www.gatewaypsychiatric.com/SFGH%20BEEC%20Course%20Material/key_dsmiv_mental_status_exam_ph.htm 
 |title=Key DSM-IV Mental Status Exam Phrases 
 |publisher=Gateway Psychiatric Services 
 |access-date=2007-06-02 
 |date=2007-05-10 
 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070630034341/http://www.gatewaypsychiatric.com/SFGH%2BBEEC%2BCourse%2BMaterial/key_dsmiv_mental_status_exam_ph.htm 
 |archive-date=2007-06-30 
 |dead-url=yes 
}}</ref>，但该术语通常俗称用来形容一种对事物超然的[[幸福|幸福]]和具有压倒性的[[滿足|滿足感]]的一种情绪波动。它也被定义为“情感状态呈现出夸张的幸福或兴高采烈”<ref>A Dictionary of Psychology in Politics & Social Sciences)牛津字典</ref>。

欣快感被普遍认为是一种病态的身体和心理状态，有时会通过使用[[精神药品|精神药品]]来达到，而不是通过正常方式得到一种人类中的精神状态。然而，一些自然的行为，如[[性高潮|性高潮]]、[[爱|爱]]，或取得比赛胜利的[[运动员|运动员]]，可诱发短暂的这种兴奋状态<ref name="DSM4phrases"/>。

欣快感也被用来指代进行某些[[仪式|仪式]]和[[冥想|冥想]]中的宗教或精神<ref>"Psychophysical Correlates of the Practice of Tantric Yoga Meditation". Corby, Roth, Zarcone, & Kopell. Archives of General Hackett, 1978.</ref>。

欣快也可以是一种心理障碍的结果。这些疾病包括[[躁郁症|躁郁症]]、[[循環性情感症|循環性情感症]]和[[甲状腺功能亢进|甲状腺功能亢进]]，也可以是头部受伤所导致<ref>{{cite web
|title=Euphoria
|url=http://www.wrongdiagnosis.com/sym/euphoria.htm
|work=Wrong Diagnosis
|publisher=Health Grades Inc.
|accessdate=2011-06-23
|archive-date=2009-01-09
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090109145207/http://www.wrongdiagnosis.com/sym/euphoria.htm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。

欣快也可以发生在某些影响神经系统的疾病患者中，如[[梅毒|梅毒]]和[[多发性硬化症|多发性硬化症]]<ref name="Body 2001">Rhodri Hayward "euphoria" ''The Oxford Companion to the Body''. Ed. Colin Blakemore and Sheila Jennett. Oxford University Press, 2001. Oxford Reference Online. Oxford University Press. 28 July 2011</ref>。

==引发欣快感的药物==
[[鸦片类药物|鸦片类药物]]是指代包括[[吗啡|吗啡]]、[[海洛因|海洛因]]、[[可待因|可待因]]在内的镇痛[[麻醉药品|麻药]]等的称呼<ref name="whoLexicon">{{Cite book|author=世界卫生组织|authorlink=世界卫生组织|title=Lexicon of alchol and drug term|publisher=World Health Organization|date=1994|url=http://whqlibdoc.who.int/publications/9241544686.pdf|format=pdf|8=|isbn=92-4-154468-6|pages=47, 49|access-date=2017-03-10|archive-date=2012-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121225004544/http://whqlibdoc.who.int/publications/9241544686.pdf|dead-url=no}} [http://www.who.int/substance_abuse/terminology/who_lexicon/en/ （HTML版 introductionが省略されている] {{Wayback|url=http://www.who.int/substance_abuse/terminology/who_lexicon/en/ |date=20130205230313 }}）</ref>，除了镇痛作用，这些药物还有镇静、强烈的欣快感、呼吸抑制、便秘等作用<ref name="pmid26811699">{{cite journal|last1=Ghelardini|first1=C|title=The pharmacological basis of opioids|journal=Clinical Cases in Mineral and Bone Metabolism|issue=3|pages=219–21|year=2015|pmid=26811699|pmc=4708964|doi=10.11138/ccmbm/2015.12.3.219}}</ref>。

[[大麻|大麻]]中含有[[四氢大麻酚|四氢大麻酚]]（THC）的成分，它的作用包括产生欣快感、不安缓解、鎮静、安眠<ref>{{cite web |author= |title=Cannabis drug profile |url=http://www.emcdda.europa.eu/publications/drug-profiles/cannabis |date=2015-01-08 |publisher=欧州薬物・薬物依存監視センター (EMCDDA) |accessdate=2016-12-28 |archive-date=2018-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180624121349/http://www.emcdda.europa.eu/publications/drug-profiles/cannabis |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[四氢大麻酚|屈大麻酚]]以及Nabiximols等一些含有大麻成分的医药品，副作用（用药目的以外的作品）便有产生欣快感<ref>{{cite report|author1=H. Valerie Curran|author2=Philip Wiffen|author3=David J. Nutt|author4=Willem Scholten=|title=Cannabis and Cannabis Resin Pre-Review Report|publisher=DrugScience|date=|url=http://www.drugscience.org.uk/assets/WHOcannabisreport.pdf|format=pdf|accessdate=2016-12-28|isbn=978-1-5272-0260-3|page=28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170531123649/http://www.drugscience.org.uk/assets/WHOcannabisreport.pdf|archive-date=2017-05-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[大麻素|合成大麻素]]也具有产生和大麻一样的欣快感<ref name="pmid26543389">{{cite journal|last1=Debruyne|first1=Daniele|last2=Le Boisselier|first2=Reynald|title=Emerging drugs of abuse: current perspectives on synthetic cannabinoids|journal=Substance Abuse and Rehabilitation|pages=113|year=2015|pmid=26543389|pmc=4622447|doi=10.2147/SAR.S73586|url=https://www.dovepress.com/emerging-drugs-of-abuse-current-perspectives-on-synthetic-cannabinoids-peer-reviewed-fulltext-article-SAR|access-date=2017-03-10|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204025630/https://www.dovepress.com/emerging-drugs-of-abuse-current-perspectives-on-synthetic-cannabinoids-peer-reviewed-fulltext-article-SAR|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[MDMA|亚甲二氧甲基苯丙胺]]（MDMA）的急性作用是产生健康的感觉、欣快感、增加对他人的共鸣。<!--P12--><ref name="pmid26070759">{{cite journal|last1=Bearn|first1=Jenny|last2=O'Brien|first2=Matthew|title=“Addicted to Euphoria”|journal=Int. Rev. Neurobiol.|volume=120|pages=205–233|year=2015|pmid=26070759|doi=10.1016/bs.irn.2015.02.005}}</ref>

[[氯胺酮|氯胺酮]]（K粉）也可以使欣快感急速增加，它随着用量增高而增高<!-- P19-20 --><ref name="pmid26070759"/>。产生高峰状态的欣快感仅需数分钟时间<ref name="pmid26070759"/>。

[[γ-羟基丁酸|γ-羟基丁酸]]（GHB）往往在娱乐场所被使用，副作用是产生性欲以及欣快感<!--P5--><ref name="pmid26070759"/>。在一些聚会上会被一些吸食者集体使用，少数人会以安眠为作用使用，但频繁的使用会产生依赖，戒断后会引起失眠<!--P12--><ref name="pmid26070759"/>。

